               <title xml:lang="ara-Latn-x-lc" type="uniform">K. al-Amr al-muḥkam</title>
               <title xml:lang="ara" type="uniform-ara">كتاب الأمر المحكم</title>
               <title xml:lang="ara-Latn-x-lc" type="full">K. al-Amr al-muḥkam al-marbūt fī mā yalzam ahl ṭarīq Allāh min al-shurūṭ.</title>
