               <!-- Editions, Translations, and Relevant Publications -->
               <noteGrp type="publications">
                  <note type="editions">Radtke and O’Kane’s translation in New Critical Essays: On the Present State and Future Tasks of the Study of Sufism (Utrecht 2005) is a critical edition in transliteration Critical edition, plus a translation into Urdu by the Ibn ʿArabī Foundation (Rawalpindi, Pakistan, 2008). Ed. Abrār Aḥmad Shāhī, but not yet published. Critical edition by Dr Moreno Giannina completed but not yet published (2018)</note>
                  <note type="translations">English translation by Rabia Terri-Harris Journey to the Lord of Power, New York, 1981 English, French and German translation by Bernd Radtke and John O’Kane: New Critical Essays: On the Present State and Future Tasks of the Study of Sufism, Utrecht, 2005 French translation by Othman Laiba and Roger Maridort: ‘Les Étapes Divines dans la voie du perfectionnment du règne human’ in Etudes Traditionelles, 1949, pp. 76-90. Italian translation by Angelo Iacovella, L’epistola dei settanta veli, Roma, 1997</note>
                  <note type="translationsEur">Spanish translation by Pedro Aguado Saiz: Viaje al Senor del Poder, Malaga, 1986. German translation by Franz Langmayr: Reise zum Herrn der Macht, Zurich, 2007</note>
                  <note type="additions_1">Publications Cairo 1986 Cairo n.d. Tehran, 1416H (in Raså⁄il Ibn ¡Arab∆) Beirut 1997 (in Raså¡il Ibn ¡Arab∆). The commentary attributed to Abd al-Karîm Jîlî is most probably not by him; on the subject, see the thesis of R. Atlagh, Contribution à l’étude de la pensée mystique d’Ibn Arabî et son école à travers l’œuvre de Abd al-Karî Jîlî, submitted at l’E.P.H.E., Paris, Décembre 2000. (MC)</note>
                  <note type="additions_2">Edited B. Radtke and trans O’Kane.</note>
                  <note type="additions_3"/>
               </noteGrp>
