               <!-- Editions, Translations, and Relevant Publications -->
               <noteGrp type="publications">
                  <note type="editions">The 1911 translation of Tarjumān al-ashwāq by Nicholson (London, 1911) contains a critical edition of the poems and the introduction, but not of the commentary. Critical edition by Dr Muḥammed ʿAlam al-Dīn al-Shuqayrī (Cairo, 1995) Critical edition and German translation in preparation by Georg Bossong of the University of Zurich.</note>
                  <note type="translations">Partially translated into English by R H Nicholson alongside his translation of the poems in The Tarjumān al-ashwāq, London, 1911. Fully translated into French by Maurice Gloton alongside his translation of the poems in L’interprète des désirs, Paris, 1996.</note>
