               <incipit type="hamdala" xml:lang="ara-Latn-x-lc">al-ḥamdu lillāh wa-kafā wa-salām ʿalā ʿibādihi alladhīna aṣṭafā wa-ʿalayka ayyuhā al-ḥamīm…</incipit>
