                  <note type="translations">English translation by Stephen Hirtenstein and Pablo Beneito: The Secret of the Names of God, Anqa Publishing, forthcoming. Spanish translation by Pablo Beneito: El secreto de los nombres de Dios, Murcia, 1996. French translation by Pablo Beneito: Les Secret des Noms de Dieu, Paris, 2010. Italian translation by Pablo Beneito, I Nomi più belli di Dio, Milano, 2011</note>
