                  <note type="additions_2">Forthcoming translation by Jim Morris in JMIAS. Tosun Bayrak’s version is not the same as Morris’s, as it comes from a later edition in Turkish rather than the original Arabic.</note>
                  <note type="additions_3">Partial translation by Asin Palacios in El Islam christianizado pp371-377. Edition Madrid, 1931</note>
               </noteGrp>
