               <!-- Stemmatics -->
               <note type="stemmatics">OY lists 24 mss., of which seven can be considered historic. The best is Shehit Ali 2813 (621H, written by Ayyūb b. Badr in the presence of IA and verified).</note>
               <!-- Related Works -->
