               <note type="stemmatics">OY lists 24 mss., of which six can be considered historic. The best are Veliyuddin 1759, which is a holograph with a samāʿ dated 617H in Aleppo, and Shehit Ali 2813 (621H, copied by Ayyūd b. Badr).</note>
